  "merge_notes": "School conflict: 2 ICT vs 1 Price Action; picked ICT by majority. One project (Education - ICT) defined C3 as not breaking candle two's high/low, while another (Education - ICT Updated) allowed wick-through but required body engulf; unified to 'does not break candle two's high/low' as more restrictive. The Foundation project added requirement that candle two must not have formed candle two closure; included.",
